{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras/mainx3-english.png?t=1737464529\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Endless Salvation\uff1a</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a puzzle-solving game that includes both co-op storylines for two players and single-player storylines.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>In the two-player co-op mode, you need to find a partner, and both of you must purchase a copy of the game in order to play.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>You don't need to be connected to the internet with your companions! You only need to be able to communicate, face-to-face, video, or phone communication.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Two player co-op mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You and your partner will respectively take on the roles of the Savior and the Wanderer, to solve puzzles across netherworld and mundane world, which consist of 18 scenes and 83 frames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After clearing the game, you can swap roles for the second playthrough, and the puzzle will be partially changed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Single-player mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will play the role of the Savior, solving puzzles in 3 scenes and 12 frames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The single-player mode is the prequel to the co-op mode, so it is recommended to prioritize completing the single-player mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features side-scrolling movement, and all you need to do is click on the scene to obtain clues, interact with characters, and solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128080/extras/\u9f99\u9f0e.png?t=1737464529\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.stea